{"tid":371354,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中甲預備組賽事   球證趕飛機提早完場","createTime":"2017-08-23T15:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T15:51:47.000Z","uid":16697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a024a280da16918978521f97f20e4c0e6b2c25c7","tid":371354,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"中甲一場預備組賽事，球證因為疑似要趕飛機，竟然提早吹停賽事。<br />\n<br />\n中甲預備組賽事，杭州綠城對梅州客家一戰，上半場只踢了40分鐘，下半場更只進行了38分鐘，原因是球證要趕飛機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據綠城發言人表示，因比賽場地五華懸地處偏遠，離周邊最近的機場有120公里距離，而且是一個很小的機場，球隊曾建議球證堤早開始賽事，因為知道他要趕一天唯一一班的航班。<br />\n<br />\n但最終這名球證都有照執法這場賽事，而賽事時間縮短未知有沒有關連。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=ecFjVELq14VfTjn935Hzlv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9fe8dc0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.goal.com/hk/news/419/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/2017/08/22/37979872/%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%B2%E9%A0%90%E5%82%99%E7%B5%84%E8%B3%BD%E4%BA%8B-%E7%90%83%E8%AD%89%E8%B6%95%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E5%AE%8C%E5%A0%B4?ICID=OP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fhk%2Fnews%2F419%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F37979872%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2594%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%2582%2599%25E7%25B5%2584%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E7%2590%2583%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%25B6%2595%25E9%25A3%259B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%258F%2590%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%25A0%25B4%3FICID%3DOP&d=ecFjVELq14VfTjn935Hzlv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=02b31143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.goal.com/hk/news/419/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83/2017/08/22/37979872/%E4%B8%AD%E7%94%B2%E9%A0%90%E5%82%99%E7%B5%84%E8%B3%BD%E4%BA%8B-%E7%90%83%E8%AD%89%E8%B6%95%E9%A3%9B%E6%A9%9F%E6%8F%90%E6%97%A9%E5%AE%8C%E5%A0%B4?ICID=OP</a>"}]}